text: Jillian Noel Hennessy (born November 25, 1968) is a Canadian actress and singer. She is most known for her roles on the American television series Law & Order, car accident attorney ad Claire Kincaid for three seasons and Crossing Jordan as Jordan Cavanaugh for six seasons. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian stage actors Category:Canadian voice actors Category:Canadian singers Category:Actors from Edmonton
